===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Jessie (Masters)}}
Jessie forms a [[sync pair]] with {{TP|Jessie|Arbok}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. Jessie became a playable sync pair on July 9, 2020.

In this game, Jessie, from [[I Choose You! trilogy|the alternate movie continuity]], somehow got transported to [[Pasio]] while chasing a {{Shiny}} {{p|Celebi}}. Unlike most characters in Pokémon Masters EX, Jessie's appearance is based directly on her {{aniseries|PTS}} incarnation, and retains her Japanese and English voice actors.

